---
title: Tuscan Veggie Bean Soup with Cheesy Pesto Toasts
description: Settle in for a cosy night with this bowl of hearty bean and tomato soup! Full of colourful veggies and classic Italian flavours, the meal gets an extra boost with these addictive grilled cheesy pesto toasts on the side. Bring on winter!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cb7cbccc445fa06713d96c2-a83bcf3b.jpg
